          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">üí°</div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-4">Tech Advisory</h3>
          <p class="text-[#64748b] leading-relaxed">
            We help startups with tech strategy, product development, and architecture decisions. CTO as a Service.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Ventures Portfolio Section -->
