          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">sanabilis.me</h3>
            <span class="bg-green-500/20 text-green-300 text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">In Development</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Health management SaaS platform. We help healthcare professionals and patients manage medical information securely and efficiently.
