            Restaurant cost management software. Ingredient control, recipes, suppliers, and AI-powered food cost optimization.
          </p>
          <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium">Coming soon</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Advisory Services Section -->
  <section id="advisory" class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-4">Advisory Services</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-[#64748b]">We help startups with technical leadership</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">üéØ</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-4">Tech Strategy</h3>
          <p class="text-[#64748b] leading-relaxed">
            We define your tech stack, architecture, and roadmap. Technical decisions aligned with business goals.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition">
