          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <a href="#contact" class="inline-block bg-[#3b82f6] hover:bg-[#2563eb] text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg transition transform hover:-translate-y-1 shadow-lg">
